<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-4131719">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Thu, 11/07/2013 - 14:12 | <a href="/news/2013-11-07/bitcoin-soars-over-300-question-arises-could-it-become-global-reserve-currency#comment-4131719" class="active">4131719</a></span>
