    <p>You know, every fucking time I hear the "its too volatile" I have to do a double-take.</p>
<p>This is fucking ZeroHedge, is it not? Are all you bastards happy with trading super-deep markets that fluctuate a few ticks each day (I'm looking at you, Eurodollar Futures), or do you actually trade markets that MOVE?</p>
<p>I know its crazy, asking if people on a FINANCIAL BLOG actually TRADE something that MOVES regularly, but what the hell, I'm feeling like asking anyway, since all the whiners keep chipping in about the fucking volatility.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

  </div>
